name: OverProtocol
description: OverProtocol is a blockchain network committed to fostering a truly decentralized ecosystem, allowing anyone to serve as a validator. Leveraging ‘Ethanos’, an innovative node optimization technology, it empowers individuals to operate full nodes from their home desktops. Driven by the vision of decentralization, OverProtocol aspires to place the power of a new internet right in your hands.
